error.message:
Error while trying to establish SSH connection to zw9dbzavm from deployer VM - Failed to connect to the host via ssh: ssh: connect to host 10.0.128.46 port 22: Connection timed out
      Possible Causes:
      a) The deployer VM /subscriptions/49d64d54-e966-4c46-a868-1999802b762c/resourceGroups/ZW9mrg-7862/providers/Microsoft.Compute/virtualMachines/ZW931ac00a1 has network connectivity issues or
      b) The input private ssh key was not valid or
      c) There is no connectivity between the SAP application layer and SAP DB layer subnets.
      Recommended Action: Ensure that deployer VM is able to connect to the host and the SSH key is valid. Also ensure that the application and the database subnet are able to communicate across all ports. If the issue persists contact support.
